title: Ep - 51 - Cary Deuber from Real Housewives of Dallas discusses the season two premiere
description:
Cary Deuber from Real Housewives of Dallas discusses the season two premiere, the relationships between cast members on the show, and why everyone thinks she keeps Botox in her freezer. Maggie Schaffer from Bravo’s show Gallery Girls explains how the show impacted her life and whether she keeps in touch with the other cast members. Annabelle DeSisto from Adderall and Compliments helps Kate review the show 90 Day Fiance: Before 90 Days.
